data.description: Perfect Mini Ranch with 2 HOMES! A 1993 stick built 1677 sqft home, 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, attached garage, deck with gazebo cover and a Hot Springs Spa. House #2 is a 2008 MFG home, approx.. 1200 sqft,3 bedrooms, 2 baths, front deck, and a detached carport. 5 acres has a 24 x 30 detached shop with high roll up doors, a 24 x 36 metal barn with animal stalls, a hay area, a really nice tack room, drive through between stalls, gated entry, and fully fenced with 5' no climb fencing.Professional pictures to be downloaded on March 19th. There is so much here for those wanting a small, but very functional mini ranch, with an in-law unit or rental.Don't let this one pass you by!
